<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
 	<meta name="description" content="InApp Banner Preview">
  	<style type="text/css">
      @font-face {
        font-family: 'Roboto';
        src: url(data:application/font-woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff2'),
            url(data:application/font-woff;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff');
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: normal;
      }

      @font-face {
        font-family: 'Roboto Bold';
        src: url(data:application/font-woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff2'),
             url(data:application/font-woff;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff');
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: normal;
    }

		body {
			background: rgba(0,0,0, 0.60);
			margin: 0;
			font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
		}

		.clearfix:after {
			visibility: hidden;
			display: block;
			content: "";
			clear: both;
			height: 0;
		}

		/* General */
		.jmb-close {
			position: absolute;
			top: -9px;
			right: -9px;
			width: 16px;
			height: 16px;
			background-color: #222;
			border-radius: 8px;
			z-index: 10;
		}
		.jmb-close-icon {
			width: 14px;
			height: 14px;
			fill: #fff;
			padding: 2px 0 0 2px;
		}

		/* Container */
		.jmb-preview {
			position: absolute;
			right: 0;
			left: 0;
			top: 0;
			margin: 12px auto 0;
			padding: 15px;
			overflow: hidden;
				background: rgba(242,228,240, 1.00);
			border-radius: 0px;
			border-style: solid;
			border-width: 0px;
			border-color:  #000000 ;
		}

		.jmb-content-container { position: relative; }

		.jmb-content {
			margin-left: 71px;
			min-height: 46px;
		}

		/* Header:Title */
        .jmb-header {
            word-break: break-word;
        }

		.jmb-header > h1 {
			margin: 0;
			color: #2B2826;
				font-size: 18px;
			text-align: center;
      		font-family: 'Roboto Bold', sans-serif;
		}

		.jmb-message-container {
			padding-top: 12px;
		}

		/* Image */
		.jmb-image {
			overflow: hidden;
			border: 0px solid  #000000 ;
			border-radius: 0px;
			-webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
			-moz-box-sizing: border-box;
			box-sizing: border-box;
			background: url(https://image.ulcm.u-next.com/lib/fe2e11737164047f7c1175/m/1/acc4f518-de8a-499f-9c3e-2334248f96e3.png);
			background-size: cover;
			background-repeat: no-repeat;
			background-position: 50% 50%;
			float: left;
			width: 56px;
			height: 56px;
		}

		/* Content:Message */
		.jmb-message {
			white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-break: break-word;

			color: #514F4D;
				font-size: 12px;


			text-align: center;
			margin: 0;
		}

		.jmb-footer {
			margin-top: 12px;
		}

		/* Footer:Buttons */
		.jmb-footer button {
			white-space: nowrap;
			overflow: hidden;
			text-overflow: ellipsis;
			padding: 12px;
			font-family: 'Roboto Bold', sans-serif;
			outline: none;
		}

		.jmb-horizontal-buttons button { float: left; }

		.jmb-button-1 {
			background:  #C694C3 ;
			border-style: solid;
			border-width: 1px;
			border-color:  #C9C7C5 ;
			border-radius: 0px;
			font-size: 9px;
			color:  #000000 ;
			-webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
			-moz-box-sizing: border-box;
			box-sizing: border-box;
		}
		.jmb-button-2 {
			background:  #03A1E0 ;
			border-style: solid;
			border-width: 0px;
			border-color:  #03A1E0 ;
			border-radius: 0px;
			font-size: 9px;
			color:  #FBFBF9 ;
			-webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
			-moz-box-sizing: border-box;
			box-sizing: border-box;
		}

		/* Phone Portrait */
		@media only screen and (min-width: 292px) {
			/* Container */
			.jmb-preview { width: 250px; }

			/* Footer:Buttons */
			.jmb-horizontal-buttons button { width: 119px; }
		}

		/* Phone Portrait */
		@media only screen and (min-width: 520px) {
			/* Container */
			.jmb-preview { width: 438px; }

			/* Footer:Buttons */
			.jmb-horizontal-buttons button { width: 213px;}
		}

		/* Tablet Portrait */
		@media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
			/* Container */
			.jmb-preview { width: 438px; }

			/* Footer:Buttons */
			.jmb-horizontal-buttons button { width: 213px; }
		}

		/* Tablet Landscape */
		@media only screen and (min-width: 800px) {
			/* Container */
			.jmb-preview { width: 438px; }

			/* Footer:Buttons */
			.jmb-horizontal-buttons button { width: 213px; }
		}

		/*
			if there is only one button shown make the button's width fit the container
		*/
			.jmb-horizontal-buttons button { width: 100%; }
  	</style>
</head>
<body>
    <article class="jmb-preview jmb-inapp-banner">
        <div class="jmb-content-container clearfix">
                    <div class="jmb-close">
                        <!-- Close Icon -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="jmb-close-icon">
                        <g viewBox="0 0 16 16" id="remove" transform="scale(0.5)">
                            <path d="M14.6 11.9l6-6c.3-.3.3-.7 0-1l-.9-1c-.3-.3-.7-.3-1 0L12.6 10c-.1.2-.4.2-.6 0L6 3.9c-.3-.3-.7-.3-1 0l-1 .9c-.3.3-.3.7 0 1l6.1 6.1c.1.1.1.4 0 .6L4 18.6c-.3.3-.3.7 0 1l.9.9c.3.3.7.3 1 0l6.1-6c.2-.2.5-.2.6 0l6.1 6c.3.3.7.3 1 0l.9-.9c.3-.3.3-.7 0-1l-6-6c-.2-.2-.2-.5 0-.7z"/>
                        </g>
                        </svg>
                    </div>

                <div class="jmb-image"></div>

            <div class="jmb-content">
                    <header class="jmb-header">
                        <h1>Assignment Reminder</h1>
					</header>

                    <section class="jmb-message-container">
                        <p class="jmb-message">Hi %%Name%%, Only 1 day left for Assignment %%assignmentTitle%% submission of %%courseName%% as deadline is %%endDate%%. Please submit it before the %%endDate%%.</p>
					</section>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="jmb-footer">
            <div class="jmb-buttons">
                <div class="jmb-horizontal-buttons">
                    <button class="jmb-button-1" type="button" title="Submit Now">
                        Submit Now
                    </button>

                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </article>
</body>
</html>
